snippet.title: Samurai Zero - Enter The Gauntlet
snippet.description:
Check out the first playable build for Samurai Zero. You will get to play the first iteration of the tutorial and run Ryder's dangerous Gauntlet. Aim for top of the community leader-boards to win free merch!

 ● Details: https://news.samuraizero.com/closed-movement-build-release-date/
